Unfortunately, over time all  PAR meters will begin to drift.

45
00:02:22,299 --> 00:02:24,496
Don't worry, it's not your fault.

46
00:02:24,496 --> 00:02:27,883
Factors such as age, usage,  and environmental conditions

47
00:02:28,091 --> 00:02:30,935
can all affect the accuracy  of every PAR meter.

